WEBVTT

01:43.080 --> 01:45.000
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL
HIDDEN LOVE BY ZHU YI

02:34.840 --> 02:35.720
BROTHER NO. 2

02:35.800 --> 02:37.280
Do you like the gift?

02:40.360 --> 02:41.800
He has really thick skin.

02:43.480 --> 02:45.880
He took such a picture
and even asked if I like it.

03:01.440 --> 03:02.600
Why is this picture there?

03:29.320 --> 03:30.400
SANG ZHI

03:30.480 --> 03:32.280
It's not clear at all.

03:32.880 --> 03:34.440
This gift is a defect.

03:43.640 --> 03:44.920
BROTHER NO. 2

03:45.000 --> 03:46.520
If you agree to let me pursue you,

03:46.600 --> 03:48.720
I'll send you an HD version immediately.

03:52.720 --> 03:53.960
SANG ZHI

03:54.040 --> 03:55.480
You wish.

04:00.840 --> 04:02.000
I had wanted to use this

04:02.080 --> 04:03.920
to speed up the courting process.

04:04.000 --> 04:05.960
I didn't expect you
to reject me right off the bat.

04:06.480 --> 04:08.000
I can only resort to this

04:08.080 --> 04:09.760
to win a chance for myself.

04:12.480 --> 04:15.760
You crafty old thing.

04:17.920 --> 04:20.519
SANG ZHI

04:20.600 --> 04:22.400
Old man.

04:22.480 --> 04:25.120
YOU CRAFTY OLD MAN.

04:28.640 --> 04:29.560
DUAN JIAXU

04:29.640 --> 04:32.120
I have to be one step ahead

04:32.200 --> 04:34.160
to deal with a young fox like you.

04:42.120 --> 04:43.400
I'm going to sleep now.

04:43.480 --> 04:44.400
Good night.

04:54.560 --> 04:55.600
BROTHER NO. 2

04:56.720 --> 04:59.160
EDIT CONTACT DETAILS

05:01.720 --> 05:04.760
SUITOR

05:16.280 --> 05:17.320
SILLY DOG

05:17.400 --> 05:19.800
Little demon, buy whatever you want.

05:19.880 --> 05:23.520
HAPPY BIRTHDAY

05:23.600 --> 05:27.560
HAPPY BIRTHDAY

05:27.640 --> 05:29.160
The pool table will be blocked

05:29.240 --> 05:30.120
if you move it there.

05:30.200 --> 05:31.200
Do you see that?

05:31.280 --> 05:32.160
Okay, boss.

05:40.280 --> 05:42.640
Sang Yan, I might be dating soon.

05:42.720 --> 05:45.560
SANG ZHI

05:45.640 --> 05:46.800
SILLY DOG

05:46.880 --> 05:48.320
Are you attending university

05:48.400 --> 05:49.720
to study or to date?

05:52.560 --> 05:53.880
Isn't it common to date

05:53.960 --> 05:55.560
during university?

05:58.600 --> 05:59.920
SILLY DOG

06:00.000 --> 06:00.840
Suit yourself.

06:00.920 --> 06:02.880
Be careful. Don't get cheated.

06:06.920 --> 06:08.200
Yes, place the stool over there.

06:08.280 --> 06:09.280
That's right. Over there.

06:09.360 --> 06:10.240
Yes.

06:17.240 --> 06:18.640
He's a bit old.

06:36.120 --> 06:37.800
- Hello?
- Don't tell me he's older than me!

06:37.880 --> 06:39.080
Lower your voice.

06:39.560 --> 06:40.800
Where did you meet him?

06:43.080 --> 06:43.960
He…

06:45.720 --> 06:47.480
He's a postgraduate student here.

06:47.560 --> 06:48.480
Listen.

06:48.960 --> 06:50.320
You should study hard at your age.

06:50.400 --> 06:51.600
Forget about dating.

06:51.680 --> 06:53.640
He can't be even one day older than me.

06:53.720 --> 06:56.360
I can't accept being addressed formally
by someone older.

06:56.440 --> 06:57.920
Even if he's one day older than you…

07:05.280 --> 07:08.000
You should feel respected
to be addressed formally.

07:25.080 --> 07:27.640
CHAPTER 16, FEELINGS

07:27.720 --> 07:29.760
WAITING FOR YOU TO DATE ME

07:52.320 --> 07:53.440
Is that from your crush?

07:59.000 --> 08:00.560
Have you decided

08:00.640 --> 08:01.800
when you will accept him?

08:06.360 --> 08:07.560
Do I need to think about that?

08:07.640 --> 08:08.880
Of course.

08:08.960 --> 08:10.240
Since he wants to pursue you,

08:10.320 --> 08:12.520
you need to decide for how long.

08:13.600 --> 08:14.920
How long should it be then?

08:16.040 --> 08:18.320
That depends.

08:18.400 --> 08:19.520
I accepted Chen Qiang

08:19.600 --> 08:21.160
not long after he started pursuing me.

08:21.920 --> 08:23.400
But it's up to you.

08:23.480 --> 08:26.800
The right time for you is the best time.

08:27.600 --> 08:30.080
I think right now is perfect.

08:33.320 --> 08:34.400
You're something else.

08:37.799 --> 08:39.840
But listen, Sangsang.

08:39.919 --> 08:41.919
You have to protect yourself.

08:42.000 --> 08:42.960
Do you understand?

08:44.039 --> 08:45.120
Weiwei.

08:46.320 --> 08:48.160
I'm actually a little worried.

08:48.720 --> 08:49.600
Worried about what?

08:50.480 --> 08:52.440
I'm afraid that he's doing it on a whim.

08:53.280 --> 08:55.160
What if he loses interest after a while?

08:56.200 --> 08:58.640
I don't think that is very likely.

08:58.720 --> 09:01.480
You two have known each other for years.

09:01.560 --> 09:03.320
Since he has decided to pursue you,

09:03.400 --> 09:05.280
that means he must be determined.

09:05.800 --> 09:06.760
What do you think?

09:07.760 --> 09:08.800
You have a point.

09:10.320 --> 09:11.240
It's okay.

09:12.120 --> 09:13.320
If you're worried about that,

09:13.400 --> 09:14.400
you can test him.

09:15.480 --> 09:16.480
I'm going to sleep now.

09:33.880 --> 09:34.800
Don't give in yet.

09:49.400 --> 09:51.280
- Here is your favorite.
- Thank you.

09:51.360 --> 09:52.760
- Your Americano.
- Here it is.

09:52.840 --> 09:54.200
Thank you, Wangwang.

09:54.280 --> 09:55.640
- Here is your latte.
- Thank you.

09:58.600 --> 09:59.640
Did you buy a new bracelet?

09:59.720 --> 10:00.640
It's pretty.

10:01.280 --> 10:02.400
What are you saying?

10:03.000 --> 10:04.080
It's a gift from her crush.

10:04.160 --> 10:05.920
- A gift from her crush?
- Really?

10:06.640 --> 10:08.120
Come on. Let me take a look.

10:12.000 --> 10:12.960
It's pretty nice.

10:13.040 --> 10:14.480
- What is this?
- Is it a mouse?

10:16.920 --> 10:17.960
It's a fox.

10:19.600 --> 10:21.400
- A fox? I couldn't tell.
- A mouse?

10:23.720 --> 10:24.880
- A mouse?
- Sorry.

10:24.960 --> 10:26.360
He has good taste.

10:32.040 --> 10:32.920
This one.

10:33.480 --> 10:34.720
Are you free tomorrow?

10:35.440 --> 10:36.760
Did your crush text you?

10:40.760 --> 10:42.120
Wait.

10:42.800 --> 10:43.920
What will you reply?

10:45.720 --> 10:46.640
Let me reply for you.

10:47.920 --> 10:50.120
Didn't we say that we would test him?

10:50.840 --> 10:52.400
It will be fine. Trust me.

10:54.680 --> 10:56.800
"No."

10:56.880 --> 10:57.760
Send!

10:58.480 --> 10:59.400
Stop messing around.

11:00.200 --> 11:01.560
What do you know?

11:01.640 --> 11:03.640
Sangsang and I talked about this before.

11:03.720 --> 11:04.640
Right, Sangsang?

11:04.720 --> 11:05.840
What did you two talk about?

11:14.960 --> 11:15.840
No.

11:15.920 --> 11:16.760
SANG ZHI

11:26.480 --> 11:27.320
Did he reply?

11:29.040 --> 11:30.480
"What about the day after tomorrow?"

11:32.160 --> 11:33.880
I might not

11:35.000 --> 11:37.480
be free either.

11:41.960 --> 11:45.080
I might not be free either.

11:49.280 --> 11:52.640
But what if he fails the test?

11:52.720 --> 11:53.880
That's impossible.

11:53.960 --> 11:54.960
He will pass the test.

11:55.040 --> 11:56.200
He definitely will.

11:56.280 --> 11:58.800
Listen, these relationship tests

11:58.880 --> 11:59.840
can go either way.

11:59.920 --> 12:01.400
Sangsang, you had better think twice.

12:07.120 --> 12:08.280
Let me ask you guys something.

12:09.800 --> 12:12.280
If you asked someone out

12:12.760 --> 12:14.240
and she replied

12:15.000 --> 12:16.640
that she might not be free,

12:18.440 --> 12:20.240
is she free or not?

12:20.720 --> 12:21.920
"Might not be free" means

12:22.000 --> 12:23.480
it depends on your performance.

12:25.720 --> 12:27.560
Why don't I call him?

12:28.480 --> 12:29.800
You don't get it.

12:29.880 --> 12:32.240
This is the appeal of love.
Do you understand?

12:32.320 --> 12:33.280
- Okay.
- What do you know?

12:33.360 --> 12:34.880
Just reply like that.

12:34.960 --> 12:37.000
Just wait. Hold back a little longer.

12:38.480 --> 12:39.920
Eat something first.

12:41.960 --> 12:43.720
Don't meddle when you don't know anything.

12:46.120 --> 12:47.360
Does that mean she's free?

12:50.760 --> 12:51.920
Jiaxu, look into my eyes.

13:05.080 --> 13:05.960
Who is it?

13:06.440 --> 13:07.440
Who might not be free?

13:08.000 --> 13:08.960
Eat your food.

13:09.040 --> 13:10.040
Don't be nosy.

13:10.880 --> 13:12.480
Something is up.

13:18.880 --> 13:20.600
Here it is! See?

13:20.680 --> 13:22.200
I told you. I knew he would reply.

13:22.280 --> 13:24.640
- What did he say?
- Let me see.

13:25.280 --> 13:26.640
How about Thursday night?

13:27.360 --> 13:29.440
"How about Thursday night?"

13:35.720 --> 13:36.640
Fine.

13:37.840 --> 13:39.960
Since he has tried three times, he passes.

13:40.040 --> 13:42.440
Hurry up. Stop being pretentious.

13:44.760 --> 13:45.600
I'm free.

13:45.680 --> 13:46.760
SANG ZHI

13:54.880 --> 13:56.000
Do I look okay?

13:56.080 --> 13:57.800
Yes, you look beautiful.

13:58.480 --> 14:00.920
There is a new noodle shop
right off campus.

14:01.000 --> 14:01.960
I heard that it's good.

14:02.040 --> 14:03.080
- Really?
- Let's go together.

14:03.160 --> 14:04.920
- Sure.
- You guys can go.

14:05.000 --> 14:06.000
Today, I…

14:07.320 --> 14:08.240
Sure.

14:08.320 --> 14:09.400
We'll try it out for you.

14:10.240 --> 14:11.800
What noodles do you guys want?

14:11.880 --> 14:13.840
I heard from Yuting that their shrimp…

14:14.400 --> 14:15.280
Sang Zhi.

14:15.840 --> 14:17.000
I'm sorry.

14:18.880 --> 14:19.920
What's the matter?

14:20.000 --> 14:22.000
Why did you start with an apology?

14:23.280 --> 14:24.120
It's like this.

14:24.200 --> 14:26.240
We just found a bug in our system,

14:26.760 --> 14:29.400
so we're all rushing to fix it.

14:30.040 --> 14:31.000
I think

14:31.760 --> 14:33.520
I won't be able to have dinner with you.

14:34.280 --> 14:37.400
Okay. Will you be working very late?

14:37.480 --> 14:39.520
Will you have dinner?
Should I get something for you?

14:39.600 --> 14:42.120
Why is there another error, Jiaxu?

14:42.200 --> 14:43.400
Jiaxu, save us.

14:44.840 --> 14:45.920
Lower your voice.

14:46.000 --> 14:46.840
Hello?

14:47.760 --> 14:49.200
You should get back to work.

14:49.280 --> 14:51.040
It's fine. Don't worry about me.

14:51.120 --> 14:52.160
Sorry about this.

14:53.000 --> 14:55.360
Remember to eat dinner, okay?

14:55.440 --> 14:56.800
Okay.

14:56.880 --> 14:57.800
Bye.

14:57.880 --> 14:59.120
Bye.

15:01.000 --> 15:02.240
It's done.

15:04.120 --> 15:06.080
I guess I'm having noodles today.

15:06.160 --> 15:07.120
Where is the shop?

15:07.200 --> 15:09.880
- Just to the right of the entrance.
- You're so dressed up.

15:09.960 --> 15:11.040
Are you going like this?

15:12.720 --> 15:14.040
Can't I eat noodles like this?

15:15.440 --> 15:16.640
I guess so.

15:16.720 --> 15:17.800
- Come on.
- Let's go.

15:20.760 --> 15:21.600
Let's go.

15:21.680 --> 15:22.560
- Bye.
- See you.

15:22.640 --> 15:23.880
- Bye.
- Bye.

15:23.960 --> 15:24.960
She's so pretty.

15:26.440 --> 15:28.080
- Hello, Jiaxu.
- What should we eat later?

15:28.160 --> 15:29.360
- Sorry.
- Pork hock with rice?

15:29.440 --> 15:32.320
Sure. Or the noodles we had last time.

15:32.800 --> 15:34.000
You're apologizing again.

15:34.080 --> 15:35.320
This time,

15:36.760 --> 15:40.200
a colleague suddenly ran into some issues.

15:40.280 --> 15:42.360
We have to change the requirements
and add functions.

15:43.920 --> 15:45.320
There's no helping it.

15:45.400 --> 15:46.320
Well,

15:47.400 --> 15:49.040
call me when you're free.

15:49.120 --> 15:51.040
You're not upset, are you?

15:53.360 --> 15:54.920
Once things settle down here,

15:55.000 --> 15:56.400
I'll take you out for a nice meal.

15:57.280 --> 15:58.240
That's all for now.

15:59.280 --> 16:00.400
Hurry up.

16:00.480 --> 16:02.600
- Right?
- Right.

16:03.240 --> 16:05.800
Didn't he say
that he was going to pursue me?

16:06.480 --> 16:08.480
Is he even trying?

16:13.480 --> 16:14.520
I don't want it!

16:14.600 --> 16:15.800
Wait for me!

16:15.880 --> 16:16.800
I'll stop.

16:16.880 --> 16:17.720
Wait for me!

16:20.160 --> 16:21.560
- What happened?
- Why are you back?

16:29.200 --> 16:30.160
You…

16:31.240 --> 16:32.200
What are you doing here?

16:32.280 --> 16:34.200
I thought you were going on a date.

16:34.280 --> 16:35.600
- That's right.
- You scared me.

16:37.960 --> 16:39.000
He canceled it.

16:39.080 --> 16:40.840
Didn't he say he wanted to pursue you?

16:40.920 --> 16:42.480
How many times has he canceled?

16:43.120 --> 16:44.920
It doesn't look like he's trying.

16:45.000 --> 16:46.400
He's busy with work.

16:46.480 --> 16:48.640
He didn't do it on purpose.

16:48.720 --> 16:50.000
So what?

16:50.080 --> 16:51.320
Can't he spare a few minutes?

16:51.400 --> 16:53.480
He should have time before and after work.

16:53.560 --> 16:55.520
He can see you if he wants to.

16:55.600 --> 16:57.360
- Precisely.
- But he really is busy.

16:57.440 --> 17:00.200
He's so busy
that he doesn't have time to sleep.

17:00.280 --> 17:01.640
It would already be our curfew

17:01.720 --> 17:03.280
by the time he gets here after work.

17:03.360 --> 17:05.560
Why are you still defending him, Sangsang?

17:05.640 --> 17:07.359
Don't you blame him?

17:10.599 --> 17:11.599
It's fine.

17:16.000 --> 17:18.079
I'm utterly speechless.

17:18.160 --> 17:20.480
Don't tell me I have to teach him
how to pursue you.

17:22.119 --> 17:23.040
Sangsang.

17:23.119 --> 17:24.319
Have you not had dinner yet?

17:24.400 --> 17:26.040
- Are you hungry?
- That's right.

17:26.119 --> 17:27.560
Where are our leftovers?

17:32.480 --> 17:35.360
- They're delicious leftovers.
- That's right.

17:35.440 --> 17:37.000
- There is fruit too.
- They're delicious.

17:37.960 --> 17:39.160
Here, take it.

17:39.240 --> 17:40.280
You haven't eaten, right?

17:41.800 --> 17:42.800
Smell it. It's nice.

17:43.840 --> 17:45.120
Don't eat that yet.

17:45.200 --> 17:46.040
Eat the hamburger.

17:46.120 --> 17:47.320
I'll have some fruit first.

17:47.400 --> 17:49.880
No, you can't have the fruit first.

17:49.960 --> 17:51.160
Why?

17:51.240 --> 17:53.640
Well, the hamburger will spoil
by tomorrow.

17:56.400 --> 17:57.720
Eat this first. It's very filling.

17:58.480 --> 18:00.480
Eat this.

18:00.560 --> 18:01.840
Take a sniff. It smells great.

18:02.880 --> 18:05.680
Currently, the character modeling

18:05.760 --> 18:07.160
is basically completed.

18:07.240 --> 18:08.080
Regarding this,

18:08.160 --> 18:10.120
we actually optimized the fluidity

18:10.200 --> 18:12.040
of the characters' techniques.

18:12.120 --> 18:13.640
Currently,

18:13.720 --> 18:16.240
we have basically completed
all optimizations.

18:17.120 --> 18:19.200
There are no issues for now.

18:19.280 --> 18:20.160
Yes.

18:20.680 --> 18:22.560
I'm sure everyone has seen

18:22.640 --> 18:23.880
how much Jia Yang has improved.

18:23.960 --> 18:24.800
You flatter me.

18:24.880 --> 18:26.880
This has been tough on you guys.

18:26.960 --> 18:28.400
Our optimization

18:28.480 --> 18:31.600
has proved to be effective.

18:31.680 --> 18:32.680
So

18:33.440 --> 18:34.800
I want to congratulate you guys.

18:36.080 --> 18:36.960
No overtime today!

18:40.360 --> 18:42.440
- Go home and rest.
- At long last!

18:43.200 --> 18:44.400
We can finally leave on time.

18:44.480 --> 18:46.400
- Yes.
- Let's go.

18:46.480 --> 18:48.560
NURSING HOME

18:51.240 --> 18:52.800
Drawing it like this won't do.

18:52.880 --> 18:54.240
What are you drawing?

18:55.960 --> 18:57.320
Sangsang, why are you back again?

18:57.400 --> 18:58.840
Did he cancel again?

18:59.680 --> 19:01.000
I was stood up again.

19:02.440 --> 19:04.200
- No way!
- Wait, what?

19:04.280 --> 19:05.840
How many times has it been now?

19:05.920 --> 19:07.280
- Was it work again?
- Don't cry.

19:09.080 --> 19:10.280
It's not work this time.

19:10.360 --> 19:12.600
But I didn't ask him about it.

19:12.680 --> 19:13.800
I couldn't be bothered.

19:14.520 --> 19:16.320
Is he pursuing her if he doesn't date her?

19:16.400 --> 19:17.520
Of course not.

19:17.600 --> 19:18.640
What is he doing?

19:19.280 --> 19:20.920
All right. It will be fine.

19:21.000 --> 19:22.800
Even without him, we are here for you.

19:22.880 --> 19:24.560
- We'll take you out for coffee.
- Yes.

19:24.640 --> 19:25.560
- No.
- Let's go.

19:25.640 --> 19:27.000
I don't

19:27.080 --> 19:28.360
feel like going out today.

19:28.440 --> 19:29.480
- Come on.
- Let's go.

19:29.560 --> 19:31.000
- Let's go. You have to go.
- No.

19:31.080 --> 19:31.960
- Come.
- No, thank you.

19:32.040 --> 19:33.480
- I'm not going.
- You have to go.

19:33.560 --> 19:35.320
- No, thank you.
- You're coming right now.

19:35.400 --> 19:36.680
C&D YIBAI ELDERLY CARE CENTER

19:36.760 --> 19:37.720
Mr. Duan.

19:38.280 --> 19:40.280
Your dad hasn't been doing well lately.

19:42.200 --> 19:44.120
I see. Thank you, Dr. Yang.

19:45.480 --> 19:46.960
He has been bedridden for nine years.

19:47.040 --> 19:49.000
His health and immunity are subpar.

19:50.200 --> 19:52.360
His pulmonary edema has worsened lately.

19:53.480 --> 19:55.920
I suggest taking him
to the hospital for surgery

19:56.480 --> 19:58.120
to remove the excess water in his lungs.

19:58.960 --> 20:01.000
Otherwise, an infection might occur.

20:01.080 --> 20:02.840
It will be even more severe by then.

20:26.400 --> 20:27.360
Do you think

20:27.840 --> 20:29.240
he will wake up?

20:31.920 --> 20:33.320
Miracles will happen

20:33.400 --> 20:34.840
as long as he is still alive.

20:39.280 --> 20:40.600
Dr. Yang, I'll let you handle

20:40.680 --> 20:42.160
the hospital transfer procedure.

20:44.240 --> 20:45.480
I'll be going then.

20:45.560 --> 20:46.440
Okay.

21:25.440 --> 21:26.280
Jiaxu.

21:27.240 --> 21:28.440
Mom, look.

21:29.160 --> 21:30.200
It's snowing today.

21:30.720 --> 21:33.120
Call your dad. Why isn't he back yet?

21:33.200 --> 21:34.240
We were going to celebrate

21:34.320 --> 21:36.120
your first place
in the city's physics contest.

21:36.200 --> 21:37.160
I'll ask him.

21:48.640 --> 21:49.560
Don't eat it yet.

21:52.440 --> 21:53.960
- Well?
- He didn't pick up.

21:55.240 --> 21:56.320
Call him again.

22:03.640 --> 22:04.560
- Dad.
- There you are.

22:08.240 --> 22:09.360
What's the matter?

22:11.880 --> 22:12.800
Did you drink?

22:14.040 --> 22:15.040
I'm done for.

22:16.200 --> 22:17.600
- What do you mean?
- I'm done for.

22:18.200 --> 22:19.120
What do you mean?

22:19.200 --> 22:20.320
Dad, what's the matter?

22:22.240 --> 22:23.360
I ran someone over.

22:26.560 --> 22:27.680
Where did it happen?

22:29.240 --> 22:31.600
At the burger shop on Renmin Road.

22:31.680 --> 22:32.680
How is that person doing?

22:34.120 --> 22:34.960
Well…

22:36.440 --> 22:37.720
No one saw it.

22:39.280 --> 22:41.560
I drank. I couldn't call the cops.

22:41.640 --> 22:43.600
Duan Zhicheng, have you lost your mind?

22:43.680 --> 22:45.200
How could you drive after drinking?

22:45.280 --> 22:46.720
Are you mad? What were you thinking?

22:46.800 --> 22:48.600
Jiaxu!

22:48.680 --> 22:50.120
Jiaxu, don't call the cops.

22:50.200 --> 22:52.080
- Don't call them.
- Dad, listen to me!

22:52.720 --> 22:54.200
We have to save that person!

22:54.680 --> 22:55.840
It will be worse

22:55.920 --> 22:57.080
if something happens to them!

22:57.160 --> 22:59.240
Dad, you can't escape from this.

22:59.320 --> 23:01.280
Zhicheng, go and turn yourself in.

23:01.360 --> 23:02.440
We'll figure something out.

23:03.480 --> 23:05.880
- I don't want to go to jail.
- Zhicheng, turn yourself in.

23:05.960 --> 23:07.040
Jiaxu!

23:07.120 --> 23:07.960
- Zhicheng!
- Jiaxu!

23:08.040 --> 23:10.040
There was a car accident
outside the burger shop on Renmin Road!

23:10.120 --> 23:13.640
- Send medical help!
- Turn yourself in!

23:13.720 --> 23:14.600
Dad!

23:15.160 --> 23:16.200
- Dad!
- Zhicheng!

23:17.600 --> 23:18.720
Zhicheng!

23:19.480 --> 23:20.560
Zhicheng!

23:22.240 --> 23:23.280
Zhicheng!

23:46.720 --> 23:47.640
You're back.

23:49.280 --> 23:50.560
Why are you still up?

23:51.040 --> 23:52.080
You're making that again.

23:52.720 --> 23:54.400
You're back late from work too.

23:54.480 --> 23:55.600
Look at the time.

24:04.200 --> 24:05.800
Did you skip dinner again?

24:06.360 --> 24:08.200
I'm not hungry. I was waiting for you.

24:09.480 --> 24:10.760
I brought noodles back for you.

24:10.840 --> 24:11.880
Put that down for now.

24:11.960 --> 24:13.240
Let's have dinner together.

24:13.320 --> 24:14.680
You're wasting money again.

24:15.440 --> 24:16.640
These?

24:17.800 --> 24:19.640
- They're inexpensive.
- Let me finish this first.

24:21.120 --> 24:22.240
- Let's eat first.
- Okay.

24:27.160 --> 24:28.080
Try this.

24:28.640 --> 24:30.880
I heard that this restaurant is good.

24:37.040 --> 24:37.920
Here.

24:42.440 --> 24:44.520
Other kids are enjoying themselves

24:44.600 --> 24:46.160
after the college entrance exam.

24:46.240 --> 24:47.440
But my son

24:48.480 --> 24:50.040
took on two jobs right after the exam,

24:50.120 --> 24:51.360
working from morning until night.

24:51.440 --> 24:52.880
It's because I'm young.

24:53.480 --> 24:55.560
Young people should endure more hardships.

24:57.160 --> 24:58.640
By the way, Mom,

24:58.720 --> 24:59.720
I asked my boss

25:00.520 --> 25:02.840
for an advance.

25:02.920 --> 25:04.800
But he can only give me
half a month's advance

25:04.880 --> 25:05.960
since I'm a newcomer.

25:07.320 --> 25:08.440
But that's fine.

25:08.520 --> 25:09.800
I'll think of something else.

25:09.880 --> 25:11.440
Just let me handle this.

25:11.520 --> 25:13.240
I'll try to borrow money
from our relatives.

25:13.320 --> 25:15.120
Stop borrowing money from them.

25:15.200 --> 25:16.240
I'm serious.

25:22.400 --> 25:23.880
Mom, I have something to tell you.

25:24.600 --> 25:25.760
What is it?

25:27.480 --> 25:28.680
After giving it some thought,

25:28.760 --> 25:30.440
I won't attend university in Nanwu.

25:31.000 --> 25:32.440
Earning money is more important now.

25:33.160 --> 25:34.280
Absolutely not.

25:34.360 --> 25:35.760
You have to attend university.

25:37.280 --> 25:40.320
Our family is in huge debt.

25:41.120 --> 25:42.400
I don't have to go to university.

25:42.480 --> 25:44.160
I will work in the morning

25:44.240 --> 25:46.200
and do part-time jobs at night.

25:46.840 --> 25:49.120
We'll pay off the debt eventually.

25:49.200 --> 25:50.880
You mustn't let our mistakes

25:50.960 --> 25:52.000
affect your future.

25:54.000 --> 25:55.200
But you know that--

25:55.280 --> 25:56.400
No buts.

25:56.960 --> 25:58.360
You have to finish university.

25:58.440 --> 25:59.600
If not,

26:01.240 --> 26:02.200
don't call me your mom.

26:06.680 --> 26:07.680
Mom, what's wrong?

26:08.240 --> 26:09.160
I'm fine.

26:09.240 --> 26:10.640
Maybe it's because I skipped dinner.

26:11.880 --> 26:14.520
My tummy is protesting.

26:14.600 --> 26:16.400
How many times have I told you?

26:16.480 --> 26:18.120
You can't skip meals.

26:18.200 --> 26:19.560
I'll get you some water.

26:34.840 --> 26:36.040
Mom, it's time to eat.

26:37.720 --> 26:39.360
Have you done the discharge paperwork?

26:41.760 --> 26:42.680
You're not leaving.

26:45.880 --> 26:47.120
What are you doing?

26:49.760 --> 26:50.800
Sit down and rest.

26:58.000 --> 26:58.880
Mom.

26:59.680 --> 27:01.040
You don't need to be discharged.

27:01.960 --> 27:04.120
I borrowed 30,000 yuan
from my university friend.

27:04.640 --> 27:07.280
You can stay here and recuperate.

27:09.240 --> 27:10.160
Jiaxu.

27:10.800 --> 27:12.360
I feel much better now.

27:13.440 --> 27:14.440
I feel like going home.

27:15.560 --> 27:16.400
I'm serious.

27:16.480 --> 27:17.760
Return the money.

27:18.760 --> 27:19.800
I already borrowed it.

27:20.400 --> 27:21.520
Your health matters the most.

27:21.600 --> 27:22.520
Rest well.

27:24.960 --> 27:25.840
My son.

27:27.240 --> 27:29.480
Aren't you tired of owing people money?

27:31.040 --> 27:32.920
We cannot stand with our heads up high

27:33.880 --> 27:35.680
until the day we pay off all our debt.

27:37.280 --> 27:39.960
I don't want you to be burdened by this.

27:41.400 --> 27:42.680
Mom, don't worry.

27:43.240 --> 27:45.960
I can earn back the money in the future.

27:46.760 --> 27:48.640
Don't overthink it.

27:48.720 --> 27:50.120
Now, have something to eat, okay?

27:50.680 --> 27:51.520
I brought you some--

27:51.600 --> 27:52.800
I'm begging you!

27:53.720 --> 27:55.520
Will you please return the money?

27:56.800 --> 27:59.040
We haven't paid off our existing debt yet.

27:59.120 --> 28:01.440
We still need to take care
of Xiaoying and her mom.

28:01.520 --> 28:03.520
We can't afford to take on more debts!

28:03.600 --> 28:05.960
What if I die one day

28:06.040 --> 28:07.760
and the debt isn't paid off yet?

28:07.840 --> 28:09.120
What will you do then?

28:09.200 --> 28:10.920
Mom, you won't die. What are you saying?

29:02.040 --> 29:03.240
What are you doing?

29:03.320 --> 29:04.960
SANG ZHI

29:05.040 --> 29:06.520
DUAN JIAXU

29:06.600 --> 29:07.560
I just got home.

29:30.840 --> 29:32.680
Hello, Jiaxu.

29:32.760 --> 29:33.960
What is it?

29:35.320 --> 29:36.320
What are you doing?

29:37.360 --> 29:38.440
I'm at my dorm.

29:41.040 --> 29:42.160
I'll go and see you.

29:45.840 --> 29:47.040
Right now?

29:48.200 --> 29:49.320
It's 8:30 p.m.

29:50.880 --> 29:52.560
That's three and a half hours left

29:52.640 --> 29:53.840
until your curfew.

30:02.680 --> 30:03.800
Okay then.

30:03.880 --> 30:05.600
I'll take you out for supper.

30:05.680 --> 30:07.040
What do you want to have?

30:07.120 --> 30:08.800
I'm fine with anything. I'm not hungry.

30:13.840 --> 30:15.560
I'll be right there. Wait.

30:15.640 --> 30:16.520
Don't wait.

30:16.600 --> 30:18.320
- Wait, I--
- Hurry up.

30:29.880 --> 30:31.320
What have you been busy with lately?

30:36.640 --> 30:38.320
Plenty of things.

30:38.400 --> 30:39.600
I have lectures to attend,

30:40.600 --> 30:42.880
assignments to finish,

30:43.360 --> 30:44.320
also,

30:45.080 --> 30:46.120
a drawing exhibition,

30:46.800 --> 30:48.040
my school club,

30:48.600 --> 30:51.040
and wait for someone to ask me out.

31:00.360 --> 31:01.440
Lately…

31:04.600 --> 31:05.440
I'm sorry.

31:06.680 --> 31:08.680
I didn't mean to keep canceling.

31:09.560 --> 31:10.720
I've just been deluged

31:10.800 --> 31:12.600
with too many miscellaneous things lately.

31:14.200 --> 31:15.480
Miscellaneous things?

31:16.440 --> 31:18.040
They're just trivial matters.

31:18.560 --> 31:19.440
They're not important.

31:26.880 --> 31:28.480
If that's the case,

31:28.560 --> 31:29.720
why didn't you ask me out?

31:33.840 --> 31:35.160
I had no idea

31:35.240 --> 31:37.520
you wanted me to ask you out so badly.

31:44.680 --> 31:45.560
Are you upset?

31:47.440 --> 31:48.280
No.

31:50.040 --> 31:50.920
I feel

31:52.560 --> 31:53.880
that you're unhappy.

31:57.960 --> 31:59.560
Are you burned out from work?

32:01.200 --> 32:03.080
No. How can that be?

32:04.120 --> 32:06.080
I'm finally having a meal with you.

32:06.160 --> 32:07.360
I'm over the moon.

32:10.280 --> 32:11.360
I'm serious.

32:13.480 --> 32:14.320
If so,

32:15.440 --> 32:16.400
give me a smile.

32:25.920 --> 32:26.760
Wait here.

32:27.480 --> 32:29.280
- Where are you going?
- Wait here.

32:35.960 --> 32:36.800
Hello.

32:36.880 --> 32:38.520
Can I make one?

32:38.600 --> 32:40.040
Hi. Do you want to make one?

32:40.120 --> 32:41.200
I would like to have a try.

32:42.360 --> 32:43.280
Thank you.

32:43.360 --> 32:44.480
It's pretty difficult.

32:44.560 --> 32:45.440
Do I do it like this?

33:11.680 --> 33:12.640
Cut it for me.

33:14.720 --> 33:15.600
Okay.

33:17.840 --> 33:18.960
Take your time.

33:28.080 --> 33:28.960
Bring it lower.

33:29.600 --> 33:31.080
Is this okay?

33:31.160 --> 33:32.240
Yes.

33:35.680 --> 33:37.120
Do you want cotton candy?

33:44.880 --> 33:46.440
- I'll pay you in a bit.
- Okay.

33:50.080 --> 33:51.120
This is for you.

33:51.600 --> 33:52.480
For me?

34:00.240 --> 34:02.040
It's as if you're cheering a child up.

34:02.680 --> 34:04.720
Yes, an old child.

34:09.320 --> 34:10.880
When I was unhappy in the past,

34:10.960 --> 34:12.239
eating sweets would cheer me up.

34:12.320 --> 34:13.600
Do you want to try it?

34:14.840 --> 34:15.800
I'll try it.

34:22.600 --> 34:23.440
Is it sweet?

34:25.880 --> 34:26.800
It's very sweet.

34:27.320 --> 34:28.280
Thank you.

34:35.679 --> 34:37.600
It's my first time
being comforted like this.

34:43.159 --> 34:44.120
Do you want to try it?

34:53.560 --> 34:54.400
Is it sweet?

34:56.840 --> 34:57.680
It's sweet.

35:08.880 --> 35:11.040
You're pretty good at making cotton candy.

35:11.720 --> 35:13.360
Have you made it for someone else before?

35:13.920 --> 35:14.800
No.

35:16.200 --> 35:17.800
So I'm the first person to try

35:17.880 --> 35:19.200
the cotton candy you made.

35:20.320 --> 35:21.240
Yes.

35:24.600 --> 35:25.800
I understand what you mean now.

35:28.040 --> 35:29.280
What do you mean?

35:32.280 --> 35:33.120
I understand.

35:36.360 --> 35:37.480
What do you understand?

35:39.480 --> 35:40.880
Haven't you agreed

35:41.840 --> 35:42.880
to be my girlfriend?

35:47.680 --> 35:49.880
When did I agree to that?

35:49.960 --> 35:52.200
Why would someone make cotton candy

35:52.280 --> 35:53.400
for an ordinary friend?

35:57.920 --> 35:58.960
- Ordinary--
- That's not all.

36:00.720 --> 36:02.160
You're wearing the bracelet.

36:10.240 --> 36:12.000
Jiaxu, you…

36:12.760 --> 36:13.920
Stop being so devious.

36:14.840 --> 36:17.120
You won't win me over like this.

36:18.000 --> 36:19.200
Then how can I win you over?

36:20.200 --> 36:21.080
You can

36:21.640 --> 36:24.800
search online

36:24.880 --> 36:27.400
or ask other people.

36:27.480 --> 36:29.480
Ask other people how to pursue a girl.

36:29.560 --> 36:30.640
How do I pursue a girl?

36:32.280 --> 36:33.760
Must you ask me?

36:34.360 --> 36:35.520
Can you teach me?

36:37.200 --> 36:39.000
Anyway, listen up.

36:39.640 --> 36:40.920
At this rate,

36:41.000 --> 36:42.360
if we're only texting,

36:42.440 --> 36:44.080
occasionally calling,

36:44.160 --> 36:46.680
and meeting up once in a long while,

36:46.760 --> 36:48.600
it definitely won't work.

36:48.680 --> 36:49.880
It's not online dating.

36:50.480 --> 36:52.200
Online dating at your age?

36:53.040 --> 36:54.200
Speaking of online dating,

36:54.280 --> 36:55.600
I suddenly recall something.

36:56.160 --> 36:57.960
- A certain kiddo had--
- Okay, that's enough.

36:58.040 --> 36:59.120
That's enough. Great job.

36:59.200 --> 37:00.440
Don't bring it up again.

37:05.560 --> 37:06.920
I was just joking with you.

37:09.960 --> 37:10.880
I'm serious.

37:11.440 --> 37:12.480
Today,

37:12.560 --> 37:14.000
I've realized my mistakes.

37:15.360 --> 37:16.200
From today on,

37:16.880 --> 37:19.680
I will be serious

37:19.760 --> 37:22.320
and work hard to pursue you.

37:25.320 --> 37:26.200
I'm serious.

37:30.360 --> 37:31.240
Great.

37:31.840 --> 37:32.920
I will look forward

37:33.680 --> 37:34.800
to your performance.

37:38.480 --> 37:39.680
Are you free tomorrow?

37:43.640 --> 37:44.880
Tomorrow morning?

37:46.040 --> 37:47.160
Not in the morning.

37:47.240 --> 37:48.640
I need to be at school.

37:48.720 --> 37:50.160
Do you have classes on the weekend?

37:50.640 --> 37:51.760
It's not a class.

37:51.840 --> 37:54.080
An alumnus is giving a sharing seminar.

37:55.880 --> 37:56.920
But…

37:57.840 --> 37:58.880
- My afternoon--
- I see.

38:00.000 --> 38:02.200
- My afternoon--
- I'll just work overtime tomorrow then.

38:03.880 --> 38:04.800
It's fine.

38:05.360 --> 38:06.360
I will keep at it.

38:10.320 --> 38:12.920
I said "but" very loudly.

38:13.000 --> 38:14.280
Don't tell me he didn't hear me.

38:21.760 --> 38:24.200
I'm excited about this sharing session.

38:24.280 --> 38:25.600
We should tell them to come.

38:25.680 --> 38:27.880
All right. I'll text them right now.

38:30.520 --> 38:31.400
Let's sit here.

38:31.480 --> 38:32.320
Okay.

38:37.480 --> 38:39.960
Text them right now.

38:40.440 --> 38:41.960
I'll ask them on WeChat.

38:51.040 --> 38:51.920
Sangsang,

38:52.000 --> 38:54.080
I can't see the blackboard from here.

38:54.160 --> 38:55.160
I'm going to sit closer.

39:02.080 --> 39:03.000
Good morning.

39:08.880 --> 39:09.800
What's the matter?

39:13.280 --> 39:14.800
Who is that next to Sang Zhi?

39:14.880 --> 39:15.880
Is that her boyfriend?

39:16.480 --> 39:17.920
I don't know.

39:18.000 --> 39:19.080
What are you doing here?

39:19.720 --> 39:21.920
Didn't you say that
there is a sharing session today?

39:22.000 --> 39:22.840
Yes.

39:22.920 --> 39:25.440
So I inquired about the time and location.

39:28.520 --> 39:30.120
Don't you have work today?

39:30.200 --> 39:31.360
I took time off.

39:35.240 --> 39:36.080
So…

39:38.040 --> 39:39.560
Are you here to keep me company?

39:39.640 --> 39:41.440
What do you mean?

39:42.000 --> 39:43.640
I just happened to run into you.

39:46.640 --> 39:47.520
Sure.

39:48.040 --> 39:50.280
You graduated from university
almost two years ago

39:50.360 --> 39:52.240
and just happened
to run into a freshman like me.

39:54.120 --> 39:55.320
And look at your getup.

39:57.040 --> 39:57.880
Do I look young?

40:03.240 --> 40:04.120
It's not bad.

40:05.480 --> 40:06.880
I'll dress like this from now on.

40:23.080 --> 40:25.280
Sang Zhi's boyfriend keeps gazing at her.

40:25.360 --> 40:26.600
He's so gentle.

40:34.720 --> 40:36.520
Why does he keep staring at me?

40:37.080 --> 40:38.720
Maybe I should pretend to sleep.

40:38.800 --> 40:41.240
I'm sleepy all of a sudden.

40:42.600 --> 40:44.440
It hasn't started yet. I'll take a nap.

40:45.760 --> 40:47.520
Why are you sleepy now that I'm here?

40:48.880 --> 40:51.280
No, I would be sleepy
even if you weren't here.

40:53.400 --> 40:54.480
Take a nap then.

41:03.480 --> 41:04.400
Go to sleep.

41:16.920 --> 41:18.480
This kiddo is pretending to be asleep.

42:21.320 --> 42:22.960
SANG YAN

42:23.960 --> 42:25.320
I think my sister is seeing someone.

42:26.040 --> 42:27.080
She's alone out there.

42:27.160 --> 42:28.360
Help me look out for her.

42:28.920 --> 42:30.240
Make sure she doesn't get tricked.

42:49.000 --> 42:49.880
Okay.
